 * Try to keep your code aligned with [Java naming conventions][3]. Only names of classes and interface should start with a capital letter.

 * In case if you&#39;ve heard from someone that usage of parallel arrays can improve memory consumption, then I would advise to examine this question dipper and take a look at questions like this https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5347338/why-use-parallel-arrays-in-java In case of such tiny arrays the only thing are disadvantages of a fragile code.


